      "title": "USA Contributor: Julie Sung",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "US Ambassador Julie Chung met President Ranil Wickremesinghe at the President's Office this morning (27).",
        "It was discussed here to take forward the existing relations between Sri Lanka and USA through a strong approach.",
        "The Ambassador also promised to cooperate in the future activities of the new government, the Presidential Media Unit announced."
